flexsurvreg(formula = Surv(tempos, status) ~ 1, data = dados, 
    dist = "exponential")

Estimates: 
      est     L95%    U95%    se    
rate  0.0490  0.0305  0.0788  0.0119

N = 20,  Events: 17,  Censored: 3
